# X / Twitter accounts to follow for /pulse.
# One handle per line (no leading @). Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# Enable the X source by setting `x: 1.0` (or higher) in
# <vault>/pulse/interests.md once this file has at least one active handle.
#
# /pulse will auto-append handles that appear in >=3 articles per run
# under an "## Auto-added" heading. Hand-edits in this file are preserved.

